{"tid":531656,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"人體冷凍技術、暫停生命、遺體保存技術：復活夢的哲學問題","createTime":"2018-01-17T05:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T06:24:09.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ad14c93c2a46f38446aa3a510528dde8339b85","tid":531656,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"科技，係由人類發展和推動的。<br />\n發展新科技的，主要都是人類中的精英。<br />\n<br />\n如果暫停生命或人體冷凍復活技術成功。頂尖的精英門，就會走晒去冷凍自己，等候未來烏托邦世界出現，結果就沒有人發展科技，科技反而倒退，因此，用科技實現復活、永生和烏托邦不可能出現。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府限制人體冷凍科技普及，咁都係精英享受，而科技又係精英推動，即係發展唔到科技。而且，社會會加劇更多不公平的情況，實際權利的貧富差距，矛盾更大，社會更不穩，爆發流血戰爭革命機會增加，於是暫停生命、人體冷凍復活、或遺體復活研究就不可能成功。"},{"pid":"dceb73bad1849dbab2d6726658498891bbdfa768","tid":531656,"uid":22736,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"似你智商有問題多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99ef8489a98047c4515ca65d03fd1930e176695","tid":531656,"uid":105400,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"On撚9，邊撚個保證未來係烏托邦，真係頂尖精英依家呢一刻已經生活無憂，仲同你慢慢等未來世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7982cce55eec43e6f5fcf252e7a7e5d97fa4a8af","tid":531656,"uid":65023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9508e693504406c98e8e040615102d3d45c30142","tid":531656,"uid":45285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"唔明樓主點FORM到精英會冷凍等烏托邦，但唔係精英先想要自己整個烏托邦~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50499d70e11d6cec3a984a7ca3e7457e34aece60","tid":531656,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"